debrief.itemText: Please answer the following questions about your experience. Click and drag the red scrollbar to move down. Do not leave any box blank. Type ‘no’ or ‘n/a’ if you don’t have a response.
Briefly describe what you were asked to do in this experiment?
debrief.response: I was asked to between two shapes to determine how many points I was going to get. In the next part of the experiment I was tasked to click the letter D if the letter on the screen was closer to A and click Z if the letter was closer to F. I was also ssked to click J if the number displayed was less than 153 and click no
